=head1 NAME

PDL::GSLSF::LEGENDRE - PDL interface to GSL Special Functions

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This is an interface to the Special Function package present in the GNU Scientific Library. 

=cut
EOD

# PP interface to GSL

pp_addhdr('
#include <gsl/gsl_sf.h>
#include "../../gslerr.h"
